Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.63,0:19:25.35,IN1-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&HFC2DEE&\blur3}あれもこれも欲しくてしょうがない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:29.31,IN1-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&H25A714&\blur3}教科書通りの綺麗事じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.31,0:19:33.15,IN1-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&H25A714&\blur3}満足できないわ　まだ食べ足りない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.39,0:19:36.74,IN1-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}誰にでも言うでしょ　"期待してる"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.74,0:19:40.95,IN1-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}前倣えで　量産型良いこちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.95,0:19:44.41,IN1-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}はみ出した私　見えてるかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.41,0:19:47.33,IN1-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}不協和音　ALL CRASH!　何もかも
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.33,0:19:50.17,IN1-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}非常事態
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.17,0:19:52.20,IN1-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}Rising noise, I want to prove
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.20,0:19:54.13,IN1-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}押し潰されそうな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.13,0:19:57.88,IN1-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}理想がせめぎあう攻防戦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:20:01.77,IN1-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}吠えてみたくて　騒めき始める
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.77,0:20:05.63,IN1-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}はね返る心臓　響く合図<チャイム>
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.63,0:20:07.51,IN1-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}Changing noise, and Make a way
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:13.25,IN1-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}模範解答は捨てて　本能のまま求めてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.25,0:20:16.99,IN1-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}邪魔するものは一片残さず
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.99,0:20:20.92,IN1-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}喰らい尽くしてやるから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.92,0:20:25.16,IN1-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}お腹いっぱい　嗚呼、ご馳走様
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.67,0:19:21.43,IN1-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&HFC2DEE&\blur3}跟随冲动不断弹奏
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.63,0:19:25.35,IN1-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&HFC2DEE&\blur3}一切都想要  无法自拔
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.35,0:19:29.31,IN1-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&H25A714&\blur3}教科书上的漂亮话
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.31,0:19:33.15,IN1-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&H25A714&\blur3}已无法满足  还没吃够
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.39,0:19:36.74,IN1-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}所有人都会说  期待着我吧
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.74,0:19:40.95,IN1-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}让我模仿前人  成为量产型好孩子
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.95,0:19:44.41,IN1-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}能看到出格的我吗
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.41,0:19:47.33,IN1-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}用不协和音  将一切击碎
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.33,0:19:50.17,IN1-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}非常事态
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.17,0:19:52.20,IN1-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}轰鸣声起  我想要证明
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.20,0:19:54.13,IN1-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}仿佛要被压垮
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.13,0:19:57.88,IN1-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}理想之间的攻防战
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.88,0:20:01.77,IN1-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}想要大声呼喊  心潮开始澎湃
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.77,0:20:05.63,IN1-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}跳跃不止的心脏  奏出警报声
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.63,0:20:07.51,IN1-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}改变杂音  让出通路
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.51,0:20:13.25,IN1-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}舍弃标准答案  遵从自我本能
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.25,0:20:16.99,IN1-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}将障碍一个不剩
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.99,0:20:20.92,IN1-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}全部咬碎吞下
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.92,0:20:25.16,IN1-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}吃饱了  多谢款待
Dialogue: 2,0:19:32.23,0:19:34.92,IN1-CH,,0,0,110,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}EAT MORE PLEASE
Dialogue: 2,0:19:36.20,0:19:39.11,IN1-CH,,0,0,110,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}IS THAT TRUE?
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-----------ED《Only one yell》----------
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.31,0:21:32.69,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)\fscx80\fscy80}One day 雨が降る日も
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.48,0:21:38.99,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)\fscx80\fscy80}聞こえていたんだ　私を呼ぶ声が
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.99,0:21:44.37,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)\fscx80\fscy80}どんな時も私のそばに居てくれたね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.37,0:21:50.21,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)\fscx80\fscy80}前を向いてまた歩いていけるように
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.54,0:21:55.50,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)\fscx80\fscy80}夢のステージに立てたらいつか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.96,0:22:05.10,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)\fscx80\fscy80}私は思い浮かべるよ　あなたの顔をきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.10,0:22:11.94,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)\fscx80\fscy80}この歌がこの声が大切な想いと繋がる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.94,0:22:15.81,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)\fscx80\fscy80}気がつけば　支えられていた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.81,0:22:22.61,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)\fscx80\fscy80}この歌がこの声が遠くまで届きますように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.61,0:22:26.99,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)\fscx80\fscy80}一つ一つ暖かな気持ち
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.99,0:22:32.29,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)\fscx80\fscy80}君の想いが希望になるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.29,0:22:38.34,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)\fscx80\fscy80}夢の先へ Only One Yell
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.31,0:21:32.69,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)\fscx80\fscy80}在下着雨的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.48,0:21:38.99,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)\fscx80\fscy80}我听到了 有个声音在呼唤我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.99,0:21:44.37,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)\fscx80\fscy80}无论何时 都有你陪在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.37,0:21:50.21,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)\fscx80\fscy80}让我有了勇气 再度迈步向前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.54,0:21:55.50,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)\fscx80\fscy80}如果有一天我能登上梦想的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.96,0:22:05.10,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)\fscx80\fscy80}脑海中一定会浮现出你的容颜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.10,0:22:11.94,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)\fscx80\fscy80}这旋律 这歌声 会连结起珍贵的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.94,0:22:15.81,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)\fscx80\fscy80}才发现是这些情感支撑着我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.81,0:22:22.61,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)\fscx80\fscy80}愿这歌 愿这声 传到遥远的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.61,0:22:26.99,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)\fscx80\fscy80}伴随一份份温暖的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.99,0:22:32.29,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)\fscx80\fscy80}你的心愿 也会成为希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.29,0:22:38.34,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)\fscx80\fscy80}朝着梦想所在 Only One Yell
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-----------OP《Glorious Days》----------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.47,0:01:14.18,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)}憧れていたステージ目指し
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:18.27,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)}あと一歩あと一歩　踏み出して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.73,0:01:23.98,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)}Anytime, Anywhere　もっと出来ると思えたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.98,0:01:26.73,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)}昨日より高く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.07,0:01:30.86,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)}涙流してぶつかって転んで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.24,0:01:34.91,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)}逃げ出しそうになったけど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.28,0:01:37.12,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)}希望抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.41,0:01:41.96,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)}諦めずにそうさここから始めよう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.17,0:01:44.83,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)}いつか　Going　羽ばたいてく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.83,0:01:47.17,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)}Going　どこまでだって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.17,0:01:50.55,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)}Going　信じ続けた道を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.55,0:01:54.64,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)}僕らはずっとこの先も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.64,0:01:58.77,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)}一緒に進んで行けるから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.77,0:02:01.60,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)}きっと　Going　叶えられる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.60,0:02:03.56,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)}Going　どんな時も
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.56,0:02:06.94,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)}Going　夢を追いかけてくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.94,0:02:11.28,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)}約束しようあの場所へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.28,0:02:18.20,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)}たどり着いて輝けるはずだから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.16,0:02:22.62,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)}Our Glorious Days!!!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.47,0:01:14.18,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)}向着梦寐以求的舞台
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.55,0:01:18.27,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)}只差一步  踏出这一步吧
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.73,0:01:23.98,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)}无论何时何地  我相信能做到更多
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.98,0:01:26.73,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)}比昨天更进一步
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.07,0:01:30.86,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)}泪水流淌  碰壁跌倒之后
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.24,0:01:34.91,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)}也会想要开始逃避
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.28,0:01:37.12,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)}但也要心存希望
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.41,0:01:41.96,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)}不放弃  就从这里开始吧
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.17,0:01:44.83,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)}总有一天  Going  展翅高飞
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.83,0:01:47.17,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)}Going  不论要走多远
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.17,0:01:50.55,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)}Going  相信自己的道路
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.55,0:01:54.64,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)}我们从今往后
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.64,0:01:58.77,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)}也可以携手共进
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.77,0:02:01.60,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)}一定  Going  是可以实现的
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.60,0:02:03.56,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)}Going  不管什么时候
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.56,0:02:06.94,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)}Going  逐梦之旅都要继续
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.94,0:02:11.28,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)}许下约定吧  前往那里
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.28,0:02:18.20,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(240,240)}到达的那天  一定能绽放光芒
Comment: 1,0:02:20.16,0:02:22.62,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,Our glorious days!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.56,0:23:42.57,Text-CH,,0,0,0,,
